Class InternalKeyBindingMBean

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.ejbca.ui.web.admin.BaseManagedBean

    public class InternalKeyBindingMBean
extends BaseManagedBean
implements Serializable
    JavaServer Faces Managed Bean for managing InternalKeyBindings. Session scoped and will cache the list of tokens and keys.
